{
  "stem": "25651.9",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they came to Palestine 1925.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother was very worried about my Uncle Itzchak, who was a very wayward boy-- young man by this time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She wanted to marry him off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The three children inherited my great-grandfather's pub in [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tarnowiec. ?] And my mother-- I told her she wasn't a stupid woman-- she organized that Perla gave my mother power of attorney.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother and-- arranged a match with Auntie Lea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She came from a family called Neustetl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Lea was a nice young woman, but she was poor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Itzchak would have never married to her because she didn't have a dowry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother-- this just will explain how she thought-- my mother arranged as a wedding present and as a dowry for Lea, she gave Lea 2/3 of the house.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was like designed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This wayward brother of theirs, Itzchak, Itzchak Engelberg, would marry because of the dowry and because the whole house would be theirs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But 2/3 of the house would be controlled by the wife, not by the brother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, this is how my mother thought out this situation, that his waywardness would have to stop.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, the war came and he was a father like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my cousins are wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a wonderful man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They all survived in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the tragedy was that she had this tuberculosis of the nerve endings and she couldn't write.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So letters from Palestine to my mother would be, 'Perla says,' and Uncle Zeev would write for my-- for his wife.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother wrote letters, you know, saying, yes, you know, we are now well-to-do, we'll pay you, and this is what we propose to do.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What do you think of it?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
